THE GAME
--------

  'Pipeliner' is a Workbench game where you have to place various
pipe sections in order to make a pipeline from the entry pipe,
located on the upper edge, towards the exit pipe, which is located
on the lower edge of the game board. The more pipe sections you
use to complete the pipeline, the more points you get...

  As you complete a pipeline, a liquid flows from the entry pipe
towards the exit pipe and then the pipe sections of the pipeline
are removed and the game continues. The unused pipe sections that
have been placed, if there are any, will remain where they are
until they get used to form another pipeline... Just avoid filling
up completely the 9 by 9 spaces board, as that will end the game.

  As you progress in the game, various special tiles will appear
to either help or hinder the gameplay...

  Have fun!

